        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I have mostly fear-kited through 180 aa points (duoing in SF) and am very sure that darkness spells always last the same amount of time. In fact I use the timer on my watch that I start when darkness lands and is set to beep when there is 20 seconds left. At that time, I recast darkness until it sticks then fear, dot, etc. This gives me plenty of time to handle double resists on darkness, and when the mob is darked, there isn't much it can do to me.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
