         I alwyas thought it was ajsut a timing issue.  I started using Astole when I fearkited, and it would break about 5 seconds before my darkness would at the time.  Two fears would break at the same time darkness would so I knew to recast darkness when astole dropped.</P><P>I think I was fear kiting Aviaks on Ogre island at the time.  I have grey flesh gloves now, and with pet exp changes the mob is always dead before darkness wears.</P><P>-DV</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
